name: FREAKOCRYXEL!
description: WOWOWOWOWOW. This is FREAKOCRYXEL! The first FREAKOLOCO! to come out of opensea. He was made for the great collage cryxelnft.art. This guy is very crazy, but he has a sweet personality. He always wants to make people happy, but sometimes this gets him into trouble. GIFS are his favorite kind of language.  If you want to please him, buy him a pack of snacks and beer and invite him to play N64.
